<subSubSection id="184579ECDE3AFAF92A59C1137A772CCB" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" type="notes">
<paragraph id="8EAE67B3788E53E51CCAD4E404B5B862" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="55410E27F089A6A50A8FF6304320B320" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">
<taxonomicName id="EAF81666D235CB6F87EEE5278E8DDD74" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Acalypha" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Acalypha lamiana" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lamiana">
<emphasis id="809C0745CF9E3E0A2D54D1C129315201" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">Acalypha lamiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was treated by 
<bibRefCitation id="26810274F5C6E62834F6697C9E5991EB" author="Leandri, J" journalOrPublisher="Notululae Systematicae" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" pagination="252 - 290" refId="B31" refString="Leandri, J, 1942. Acalypha. Contribution a l'etude des Euphorbiacees de Madagascar (VI). Notululae Systematicae 10: 252 - 290" title="Acalypha. Contribution a l'etude des Euphorbiacees de Madagascar (VI)." volume="10" year="1942">Leandri (1942)</bibRefCitation>
as a form of 
<taxonomicName id="093702F1AEED9C50FF305747F3139D07" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." infraspecific-rank="var." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. reticulata var. urophylla" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="variety" species="reticulata" variety="urophylla">A. reticulata var. urophylla</taxonomicName>
(Boivin ex Baill.) 
<normalizedToken id="2F93054DBF9EABC40405F71C82457D5C" originalValue="Müll">Muell</normalizedToken>
.Arg. (treated here as 
<taxonomicName id="6F6A59AF448871BC830F26816A03A2BD" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. urophylla" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="urophylla">
<emphasis id="57EC568C6DCB1E214F1CBF9BB85C71C7" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">A. urophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). After studying the numerous type collections, it seems clear to us that 
<taxonomicName id="786F2A66A974D75CC4C746B13C3CD625" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. lamiana" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="lamiana">
<emphasis id="CEEC4BB09BCA2307FD19D8B5524BD8DD" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">A. lamiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
must be considered as a distinct species. 
<taxonomicName id="B107BD72574E57964C75CFEEE240BA1C" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. lamiana" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="lamiana">
<emphasis id="7CD65F4B3D8B92FA8AA3D058C0F53C7A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">A. lamiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName id="FAB08A9E02183EC593370D79DFAE90E8" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. urophylla" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="urophylla">
<emphasis id="62B2BB09A84CDA8A9F0DB9BC9E0FBF1E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">A. urophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
mainly by the leaves that are rounded at the base and reddish at the margins and its subentire, eglandular female bracts vs. leaves that are usually acute at the base and not reddish at the margins and dentate female bracts with small sessile glands at margins, in 
<taxonomicName id="66853103B72F1E88D0F4C2B7A156F832" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. urophylla" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="urophylla">
<emphasis id="A92FD8385A6BCFB88527C929FF721708" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">A. urophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1AD243A3F578404E7986539C48D6E642" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">
One of the mentioned syntypes, 
<emphasis id="FF68868E0E53241B78F2554F452257B0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">
Perrier de la 
<normalizedToken id="A71ACEA6DEA4899ECFA7599F9234F8FF" originalValue="Bâthie">Bathie</normalizedToken>
9817
</emphasis>
, was wrongly transcribed by 
<bibRefCitation id="84611C3DAA2A2481E1E2355AAB44901F" author="Leandri, J" journalOrPublisher="Notululae Systematicae" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" pagination="252 - 290" refId="B31" refString="Leandri, J, 1942. Acalypha. Contribution a l'etude des Euphorbiacees de Madagascar (VI). Notululae Systematicae 10: 252 - 290" title="Acalypha. Contribution a l'etude des Euphorbiacees de Madagascar (VI)." volume="10" year="1942">Leandri (1942</bibRefCitation>
: 263) as 
<normalizedToken id="453B31D585AE3C04AA414F628A0C0F2A" originalValue="“8917”">
&quot; 
<emphasis id="41DBFCA04B4B668248B86AA21E9AD3D0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">8917</emphasis>
&quot;
</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
